      "<b>Banana Juice Cordial</b><br>3 Bananas<br>Pinch of Citric Acid<br>Clarify with Pectinex<br>Citric Acid @3% by weight",
      "<b>Coconut Cloud Float</b><br>2:1 Coconut Milk : Thick Cream<br>Pinch of Salt<br>Vanilla Extract"
    ],
    "notes": "Concept originally from 'MOKU', Sydney - 'Ba-la-la' cocktail"
